[The 1st article in the USA subsection helps explain why this HPAI is moving so fast across North America.

We have many times mentioned biosecurity as being the key to prevention with this virus. While we understand many people practice good biosecurity, still sometimes this virus gets through. Building a tough, impermeable barrier to an unseen, deadly virus is very tough. Please continue to be resolute at maintaining biosecurity.

This virus is still marching on. We hope cooler weather and the end of fall migration will bring a stop to this virus. - Mod.TG

